args: La la laaaa... Aaaand, we're done!\nNow I just need an opponent.
If I may ask, why did you draw\nthat large circle on the ground?
This, Estelle, is a ＂ring.＂ It is where\ncompetitions take place in the eastern\nsport of sumo wrestling.
I didn't know you were interested\nin eastern sports.
I'm interested in anything that\nmight prove useful in training!

Sumo wrestling is all about intense
combat, which HAS to be great for
building up strength. I've been eager
to try it for a while now.
And you decided to do it here?
Exactly! See, when you're wrestling,\nyou fall over a lot, so if the ground\nisn't soft, that could be dangerous.
Ah, so the beach is perfect for it.
And now that I have my perfect ring,\nI need an opponent. ...Hint. ...HINT.
Er, I'm not really much for wrestling,\nbut I suppose I can try it.
Right then! Let me give you a rundown\nof how this is done.
First, I need you to join me in the ring.
Now we stand in the center with\nour backs to one another.
Perfect. And finally, we fight with\nour glutes to determine a victor!
Okay, this all makes sen—Wait.\nSay that last part again?
Each of us uses the force and strength of\nour gluteus maximus to drive the other\none straight out of the ring.
Of all the lewd and smutty...\nThis can't POSSIBLY be a sport!
Of course it is! ...It's also great for\nbuilding both your core and hips.
You can try to justify its inappropriate\nnature all you like, but I won't do it!
What do you say to a round of sumo?\nIt's great for building lower body strength!
I've never heard of sumo before,\nbut I'd be happy to try—
STOOOOP! Don't say one more word until\nyou hear the details of the filthy, immoral\nbehavior she has in store for you!
Er, this is getting a little weird.
She wants you to wrestle with your...\nyour BACKSIDE!
Okay, maybe a lot weird.\nStill, it IS a form of training, yes?
And an effective one at that!
Well, if Celliera is so serious about a\ntraining method, it must be legitimate.
How am I the one in the wrong here?!
...No, there's no way that's true.\nSHE is the crazy one!
Now then! Once you enter the ring,\nturn your back to me and—
Hold on! We aren't done talking!
Fine! I'll do it! I'll...butt wrestle.
No idea what changed your mind,\nbut frankly, I don't really care.\nNow get into the ring, missy!
Urgh... I shouldn't have said that...\nBut public decency sometimes demands\none to make the ultimate sacrifice!
Well done, for a beginner! But now...\nHah! Hah! HAAAAAAAAH!
This indecent sport should not exist,\nbut if I'm competing, I am going to WIN!
BEHOLD THE POWER OF MY BUTT!\nHAH! HAH! HAAAAAAAH!
Goodness, what glutes she has...\nFinally, a true challenger approaches!
You both left the ring at the same time!
Oh well. Guess this round is a dra—
And yet, it makes sense when you\nconsider that a slapping motion\nall begins in the hips.
I don't know about all that...
You must teach me about slapping!\nI might be able to utilize it in my\nlower-body training.
Ha ha! Celliera is nothing if not devoted.
Perhaps I was a bit hasty when I branded\nthis whole event as madness.
I'll be happy to teach you everything\nyou want to know, Celliera.
And I will be happy to learn!
All right, time for another round!\nBut this time, I want to take YOU on,\nPrince {player_name}!
